                          CORPS "Cyber" System 0.3.0
                          ==========================

This package contains the "Cyber" roleplaying system for use with CORPS -
The CORBA Roleplaying System. It is located in the world of the 2060s.
Technology has made great advances and magic has been returned.

Requirements
------------

To do anything useful with this, you need at least the package corps-core.

Installing
----------

See the file INSTALL for information about compiling and installing the
package.

